# qodana-go — Qodana Ultimate for Go/GoLand (image name = repoName). Feed code QDGO, PUBLIC feed: this
# `.env` OMITS QD_DISTRIBUTION_FEED and relies on lib/dist.dockerfile's public-feed default. Builds on
# the DHI golang language base (Go PRE-BAKED, but NO node), so — unlike qodana-js's node base — it
# LAYERS the node toolchain (NODE_MAJOR) + the in-place eslint pin for JS/TS support, exactly like the
# source qodana-cli go.Dockerfile. SAME key set as qodana-jvm (dist + node toolchain). NO DIST_BASE_STAGE
# (node+eslint are in-place on base; the dist FROMs base). The golang base does NOT occupy uid 1000
# (empirically: /etc/passwd has only root/nonroot/_apt/nobody), so qodana-go keeps base.dockerfile's
# DEFAULT uid 1000 and sets NO uid keys/build args — only qodana-js needs the 1001 shift. eslint is
# pinned in lib/toolchain/eslint/package.json (renovate-tracked), NOT here. Pins are the concrete values
# in docs/phase-0-decisions.md; EnvContractTest asserts byte-identity for QD_VERSION/QD_BUILD/
# QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE and the golang base digest.
QD_LINTER_SLUG=qodana-go
QD_VERSION=2026.1
QD_BUILD=261.25884
QD_RELEASE_TYPE=release
QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE=GO
QD_BASE_IMAGE=dhi.io/golang:1.26-debian13-dev@sha256:d1295e34ae659bfd57c305d67ec5177c15694fb82f25d98aee76d0ae08ef8ad1
CLI_BINARY=qodana
CLI_VERSION=2026.2
CLI_OS=linux
CLI_ARCH=amd64
NODE_MAJOR=20
TINI_VERSION=v0.19.0
TINI_ARCH=amd64
TINI_SHA256=93dcc18adc78c65a028a84799ecf8ad40c936fdfc5f2a57b1acda5a8117fa82c
